- Lalu?

66
00:06:00,847 --> 00:06:02,306
Apa yang akan kau lakukan seorang diri?

67
00:06:17,447 --> 00:06:18,823
Aku mau pastikan sesuatu.

68
00:06:19,407 --> 00:06:20,908
Sepertinya aku tahu pelakunya.

69
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:24,996
<i>Tabrak lari?</i>

70
00:06:33,212 --> 00:06:35,340
- Park Saeroyi?
- Benar, Pak.

71
00:06:35,965 --> 00:06:38,009
Kemarin malam dia dirawat di rumah sakit

72
00:06:39,218 --> 00:06:40,720
dan sekarang masih belum sadar.

73
00:06:43,598 --> 00:06:44,682
Panggil Geun-soo.

74
00:06:46,351 --> 00:06:47,810
Direktur Jang hari ini...

75
00:06:49,687 --> 00:06:51,064
